Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.88,0:00:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然難得從媽媽那裡得到了補助券
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.30,0:00:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是兩張不能去抽獎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.06,0:00:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有中獎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.98,0:00:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.56,0:00:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像我也有一張
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.47,0:00:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,nice 葵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.55,0:00:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.85,0:00:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.53,0:00:24.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.88,0:00:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 如果中了什麼獎的話 要分一半給我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.66,0:00:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.67,0:00:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴 這次的考試假期 有什麼計劃嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.62,0:00:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並沒有什麼特別的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.39,0:00:44.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 下週就是智花她們的修學旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.24,0:00:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到跟考試假期剛好重疊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.05,0:00:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明打算在假期裡多教教她們的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:00:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因為那個年齡的吸收能力很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.86,0:00:59.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以很值得去教她們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.71,0:01:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是剛開始當五年級隊的教練 對此深有體會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.85,0:01:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 智花他們的修學旅行去哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.24,0:01:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是三天兩夜 去京都的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊 京都嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你們!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.27,0:01:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特別獎 秋之京都旅行 兩人券
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.65,0:01:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中頭彩！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.26,0:01:29.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,------------------OP--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:04.28,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\pos(135,343)}葵的勝利?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換洗的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.36,0:03:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗面奶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.21,0:03:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防暈藥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指甲刀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,針線包
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胃藥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.07,0:03:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼藥水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,止痛藥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.74,0:03:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 酸痛藥布呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 又得重來一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部長 你塞進去又拿出來已經是第五次了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.54,0:03:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和大師兩個人去旅行心情很激動 這我可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是這樣 只不過是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶然抽中了大獎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.44,0:03:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抽獎之前又約定了如果中獎了就平分而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.37,0:03:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部長 這次真是很恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們為你的京都旅行所挑選的餞別禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.01,0:03:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,餞別什麼的 太誇張了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 收下吧 部長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.05,0:03:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是經常受部長照顧的我們的一點心意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿園 阿寺 謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:02.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,內 內 內… 內褲？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修學旅行都準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真帆才是 準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.81,0:04:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經把行李確認了5次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.84,0:04:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完美 Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 真是吃了一驚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到長谷川前輩跟葵前輩也在同一天去京都旅行什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是讓人感覺到這就是命運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.08,0:04:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命運什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.45,0:04:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿昴說過會在自由時間跟我們一起玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪裡去哪裡好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.46,0:04:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向只要能跟哥哥在一起 去哪裡都行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經等不及了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去創造很多美好的回憶吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦~！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了? 臉好紅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.66,0:05:23.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是發燒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒… 沒… 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎 是這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.80,0:05:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過真是好啊 能和葵在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.05,0:05:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是葵的話 我一定不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴… 這麼重視我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了啊 除了葵之外 我都不會考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.05,0:05:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴 我也是對昴…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:05:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 跟男生兩個人去旅行什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子的媽媽一定不准許
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是青梅竹馬 這麼信任我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是其他女孩的話一定不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:11.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到京都之後去哪裡好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:16.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也得去聽聽智花她們的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.47,0:06:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然跟大家玩是好 但也得給我們兩個人一點時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.43,0:06:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？ 你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.76,0:06:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴大哥 葵姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.77,0:06:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.93,0:06:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 去哪裡好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.61,0:06:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先去清水寺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起在舞台上跳水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:42.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦~ 日向是初體驗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險的事不能做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.93,0:06:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好厲害啊 好高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好危險啊 真帆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥哥 日向要跳了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.50,0:07:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳躍是禁止的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿昴 來拍照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.65,0:07:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡好像可以借出「源氏物語」的衣服和劇本
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後可以拍攝紀念電影
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 真好真好 我們去拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴… 源氏大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.36,0:07:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 智… 紫之上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:08:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿昴 啊不對 源氏大人 我是夕顏君哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光之君 妾一直以來都很想見您
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好 源氏之君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥哥 日向是新娘哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 歎為觀止 多麼美麗的幼女們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.63,0:08:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幼…幼女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴 你在說些什麼奇怪的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.03,0:08:26.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是沒辦法的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.51,0:08:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劇本上是這麼寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.76,0:08:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.37,0:08:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你穿起來很合身嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.22,0:08:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴也很合身 很帥…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴也好帥呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常合身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的光源氏一定也是像您這樣威嚴可敬的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太帥了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦~ 大哥哥是帥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.03,0:09:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.66,0:09:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光源氏就是把10歲的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.08,0:09:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照自己的喜好培養長大為妻的那個故事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.93,0:09:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴果然也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.06,0:09:15.33,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,只是個人的感想而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這裡 這個地方是一定要來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,youjiya…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs32}牙籤店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.16,0:09:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幼兒店？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.16,0:09:32.56,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,註：日語中牙籤和幼兒音同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴大哥 我是幼兒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幼兒幼兒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是幼兒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.73,0:09:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幼兒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥哥 我是幼兒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 該選哪個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.62,0:09:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 昴 絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:51.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:56.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸拜託我買些牙籤寄到夏威夷去 不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:09:59.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到連住的酒店都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.64,0:10:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是湊巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.37,0:10:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 為什麼你們會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是偶然而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.90,0:10:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 不好說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可別做奇怪的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不會做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天房間已滿 開不了別的房間了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過仔細想想畢竟是配對旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.67,0:10:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個人住一個房間是理所當然的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 在！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗澡真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.61,0:11:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想快點去洗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竹中 我們一起在酒店裡探險吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.93,0:11:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.85,0:11:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 有東西掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.64,0:11:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 竹中 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.58,0:11:40.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H00006A&\fs17\bord0\frz28\pos(340,370)}胸圍：部內排名第二位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.58,0:11:40.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H00006A&\fs17\bord0\frz28\pos(430,410)}給昴的寄語：想更多更多地和大哥哥在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:44.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗…洗澡？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一整天都在到處走 肯定流了不少汗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:52.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去買飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,內 內 內…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種內衣叫我該怎麼穿…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上那個的話 就能確保讓他興致勃勃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:44.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你好運
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不 不可能 怎麼可能穿這種…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:51.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種狀況 該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這條內褲 該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去 是無法入睡的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 昴也睡眠不足嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.36,0:13:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 有些比較在意的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.82,0:13:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 昴也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也在為我擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.64,0:13:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿茶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:44.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.19,0:13:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天晚上 把你所持的內褲還回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.90,0:13:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.19,0:13:57.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.95,0:14:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥哥的表情好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.09,0:14:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不 各位早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天晚上我明明一直等著阿昴會來我的房間玩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.19,0:14:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天晚上一定要來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.06,0:14:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 剛才是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能否給我說明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是字面意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.93,0:14:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天晚上你撿到的真帆的內褲 今天晚上要還回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你會知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說你怎麼知道那是真帆的內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.02,0:14:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿昴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我看到真帆是把內褲落在那裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你就不能當即撿起來還回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想還回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.01,0:14:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是當時朋友正好叫我 我就慌張地把它藏起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:41.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.72,0:14:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 為什麼那條內褲又會被我撿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.80,0:14:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 我也有了 用骯髒的手段把別人拖下水的經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你丫的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.79,0:14:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然現在在你那裡 你已經沒有權利指責我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:14:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也會幫助你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:02.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚你要去還 真帆的內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.78,0:15:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該說幫助的人是我 明明是你先撿到的內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.42,0:15:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在 女生們正在洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你趁這個機會潛入 把內褲還回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美星姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.84,0:15:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽多野老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.18,0:15:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想去偷窺女生洗澡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.10,0:15:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.87,0:15:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是在交流討論籃球練習的經驗 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一成不變的籃球癡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 比和葵做些偷雞摸狗的事要好得多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴和我一樣 都是令人放心的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你哪裡令人放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為了和美星玩 帶了好多道具來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待會一起好好享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.25,0:16:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…昴 如果親戚里出了殺人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.65,0:16:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐就要你多多關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍住 美星姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.39,0:16:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浪費了時間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你帶上了內褲沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:36.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.08,0:16:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.09,0:16:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,內褲！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做什麼呢 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我快點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.57,0:17:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊是女浴池
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 今天也走了很多路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.01,0:17:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫泉溫泉 露天浴場
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 喂 別看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.93,0:17:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不准看 要是你看了這輩子我都不會原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我的內褲哪去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許就像合宿的時候 夏陽偷偷拿走了一樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼傻話呢 是真帆自己不小心掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修學旅行明天就結束了呢 真是好開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.84,0:18:08.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三天兩夜 真是轉瞬即逝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天晚上還有時間 阿昴也一定會來玩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創造更多更多更多的回憶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦~ 日向想和哥哥創造很多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.04,0:18:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴大哥現在在哪裡 又在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一點 一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然好不容易把內褲拿回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.46,0:18:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你磨磨蹭蹭的 大家都已經洗完澡回來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.65,0:18:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法了 那就假裝去她們的房間玩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁機把內褲還了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種聽天由命的方法會順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包在我身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:54.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿昴 歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏陽為什麼也來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不是喜歡才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.39,0:19:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 這什麼狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可不是為了做這種事才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.64,0:19:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我瞭解 現在就創造時機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.32,0:19:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竹中 就靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.29,0:19:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍不住出來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.78,0:19:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來一決勝負 我可不會手軟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.57,0:19:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦~ 不會放水哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長谷川前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,低手上籃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盲傳球？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(415,432)}no look pass
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴大哥 nice shot
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.54,0:20:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦~ 好帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過現在是扔枕頭大戰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿昴真是個籃球癡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.33,0:20:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 部長 我們的餞別禮物如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.74,0:20:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定成功了吧
